    "body": "Two ideas in my mind:\r\n1. Convert the hex to dec, so the node won't crash\r\n2. Be more precise with the error message, as the current one is misleading\r\n\r\nis it an expectation that hex type is not allowed to be passed as balance? \r\nIf no, then I could drop a PR for the 1st option. Otherwise, 2nd\r\n\r\nWould like to hear your thoughts",
