    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "To expand on what @alcuadrado said: I think we should replace the `t.string` here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/0b44fc42f9af05a0318be643808fea6f29c079c4/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/core/config/config-validation.ts#L88\r\n\r\nwith a io-ts codec that checks that the value is a string with a proper decimal value. An example of something like that is this one:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/0b44fc42f9af05a0318be643808fea6f29c079c4/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/core/config/config-validation.ts#L68-L81\r\n\r\n`io-ts` is not very intuitive, and its documentation is... not very pedagogic, but it's not that hard to play it by ear.\r\n\r\nThis also needs tests. They are under the `test/internal/core/config/config-validation.ts` file.",
